    <string name="faq_q1">How to connect?</string>
    <string name="faq_a1">Simply tap the power button on the home screen to connect to the fastest available node.</string>
    <string name="faq_q2">Why is it slow?</string>
    <string name="faq_a2">Connection speed depends on your physical distance from the selected node and the node\'s current load.</string>
    <string name="faq_q3">Is my data secure?</string>
    <string name="faq_a3">Yes, we use industry-standard encryption protocols (VLESS/VMess) to ensure your traffic is protected.</string>
